To fix the extra space a BR produces in TorBrowser, use this style for the card-text:

.card_body{
        line-height: 20px;
}

Better set line-height to 19px, that was the default value before.

And to set a unique font for all browsers set:

body{
  font-family: Bitstream Vera Sans;
}
